column2: "Sorry, <%sp_name>, but I need to borrow your body a little more."
"I'm directly hacking the Support Partner though Xion, so admittedly, it's a little dangerous."
"If Luther or otherwise were to look into the logs, they might notice something, but we don't have a choice."
"Even with the risk, there's meaning in what I need to show you at this time."
"In the last operations, it's said that everyone who had gone missing had been finished off by Darkers."
"Kind of convenient, don't you think? Anything can be easily attributed to Darkers."
"It's a little further ahead, let's keep going."
